---
import { Plus } from 'lucide-react';
---

<section id="faq" class="w-full px-4 sm:px-8 py-16 lg:py-24 bg-bgMain brutal-border-b relative z-10">
	<div class="max-w-[1000px] mx-auto observe-block">
		<div class="text-center mb-16">
			<span class="text-[12px] font-mono font-bold text-primary uppercase tracking-widest block mb-4">[ 06. Intel ]</span>
			<h2 class="text-fluid-h2 font-bold uppercase leading-tight">
				<span class="reveal-overflow"><span class="reveal-text block">Common Questions</span></span>
			</h2>
		</div>

		<div class="stamp-item delay-100 flex flex-col border-t-[3px] border-black">
			<details class="group border-b-[3px] border-black bg-surface">
				<summary class="flex justify-between items-center py-6 sm:py-8 font-bold uppercase text-[16px] sm:text-[20px] cursor-pointer outline-none hover:text-primary transition-colors pr-4">
					How long does a project take?
					<Plus className="faq-plus w-6 h-6 sm:w-8 sm:h-8 flex-shrink-0 ml-4 border-2 border-black rounded-full p-1 group-hover:border-primary transition-transform duration-200" />
				</summary>
				<div class="faq-content pb-8 text-[16px] sm:text-[18px] text-textSecondary font-[500] pr-4 max-w-3xl">
					Most custom modernization projects take between 3 to 6 weeks, depending on the complexity and scope.
				</div>
			</details>
			<details class="group border-b-[3px] border-black bg-surface">
				<summary class="flex justify-between items-center py-6 sm:py-8 font-bold uppercase text-[16px] sm:text-[20px] cursor-pointer outline-none hover:text-primary transition-colors pr-4">
					Do you work with WordPress?
					<Plus className="faq-plus w-6 h-6 sm:w-8 sm:h-8 flex-shrink-0 ml-4 border-2 border-black rounded-full p-1 group-hover:border-primary transition-transform duration-200" />
				</summary>
				<div class="faq-content pb-8 text-[16px] sm:text-[18px] text-textSecondary font-[500] pr-4 max-w-3xl">
					Yes, I can repair and optimize existing WordPress sites, or migrate you to a faster, modern platform if needed.
				</div>
			</details>
			<details class="group border-b-[3px] border-black bg-surface">
				<summary class="flex justify-between items-center py-6 sm:py-8 font-bold uppercase text-[16px] sm:text-[20px] cursor-pointer outline-none hover:text-primary transition-colors pr-4">
					Can you fix my existing website?
					<Plus className="faq-plus w-6 h-6 sm:w-8 sm:h-8 flex-shrink-0 ml-4 border-2 border-black rounded-full p-1 group-hover:border-primary transition-transform duration-200" />
				</summary>
				<div class="faq-content pb-8 text-[16px] sm:text-[18px] text-textSecondary font-[500] pr-4 max-w-3xl">
					Yes. Many of my clients come to me with broken themes, slow load times, or layout issues. I can audit your current setup and repair it without needing to start from scratch.
				</div>
			</details>
			<details class="group border-b-[3px] border-black bg-surface">
				<summary class="flex justify-between items-center py-6 sm:py-8 font-bold uppercase text-[16px] sm:text-[20px] cursor-pointer outline-none hover:text-primary transition-colors pr-4">
					How much does it usually cost?
					<Plus className="faq-plus w-6 h-6 sm:w-8 sm:h-8 flex-shrink-0 ml-4 border-2 border-black rounded-full p-1 group-hover:border-primary transition-transform duration-200" />
				</summary>
				<div class="faq-content pb-8 text-[16px] sm:text-[18px] text-textSecondary font-[500] pr-4 max-w-3xl">
					Technical rescue projects start around $750, while full custom modernization starts around $5,000+.
				</div>
			</details>
			<details class="group border-b-[3px] border-black bg-surface">
				<summary class="flex justify-between items-center py-6 sm:py-8 font-bold uppercase text-[16px] sm:text-[20px] cursor-pointer outline-none hover:text-primary transition-colors pr-4">
					Do you offer ongoing support?
					<Plus className="faq-plus w-6 h-6 sm:w-8 sm:h-8 flex-shrink-0 ml-4 border-2 border-black rounded-full p-1 group-hover:border-primary transition-transform duration-200" />
				</summary>
				<div class="faq-content pb-8 text-[16px] sm:text-[18px] text-textSecondary font-[500] pr-4 max-w-3xl">
					Absolutely. I offer monthly retention packages to keep your site updated, secure, and running fast so you can focus on your business.
				</div>
			</details>
			<details class="group border-b-[3px] border-black bg-surface">
				<summary class="flex justify-between items-center py-6 sm:py-8 font-bold uppercase text-[16px] sm:text-[20px] cursor-pointer outline-none hover:text-primary transition-colors pr-4">
					Can you help with SEO after launch?
					<Plus className="faq-plus w-6 h-6 sm:w-8 sm:h-8 flex-shrink-0 ml-4 border-2 border-black rounded-full p-1 group-hover:border-primary transition-transform duration-200" />
				</summary>
				<div class="faq-content pb-8 text-[16px] sm:text-[18px] text-textSecondary font-[500] pr-4 max-w-3xl">
					Yes. All my builds are technically optimized for search engines by default. I can also help with ongoing performance tweaks and technical SEO strategy to improve your rankings over time.
				</div>
			</details>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
